creator: FiveSixty
descriptionHtml:
REBIRTH OF THE WARRIOR

Welcome to the AmaZulu Football Club Application. It is with Usuthu-Pride that you support us and it is with the same pride that we want to support you.

This Application is exactly that; not only does it contain all you need to know about your favourite football team, their fixtures and standings but it also includes our thanks to you in the form of Special Offers, Benefits and Rewards.

Join our club today, download the AmaZulu Football Club Application!

descriptionHtml:
Hebe! Usuthu! Welcome to the #HebeNation and the official app of the AmaZulu Football Club.

Get access to all you need to know about your favourite football team; fixtures, standings, exclusive content, supporter benefits and so much more!

Join our club today as a member, download the AmaZulu Football Club App and be part of the USUTHU NATION!
